metadata.name: Sun Dune
metadata.description:
I love shooting silhouettes. While on a tour to Sam Dunes in Jaisalmer, Rajasthan, India, I saw a herder going with his herd of 2 camels. I quickly changed my position to align them against rising Sun and the clouds in sky seem to complete the composition. 

Camera: Canon 5D Mark III
f/8, 1/320, ISO 100
Image Dimensions: 6500x1047 pixels
